One of \code{"DC"} (Decrement and Cancel), \code{"CO"} (Cancel Oldest),
\code{"CN"} (Cancel Newest), \code{"CB"} (Cancel Both).}

\item{\code{remark}}{Character or NULL; order remarks or notes (max 20 ASCII characters).}

