\subsection{Method \code{get_order_by_id()}}{
Get Stop Order by Order ID

Retrieves full details for a single stop order using its KuCoin-assigned
order ID. Returns order parameters, status, trigger price, and timestamps.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Authenticated GET with the order ID in the URL path.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Returns a \code{data.table} with all order fields as columns.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/stop-order/\{orderId\}}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/spot-trading/orders/get-stop-order-by-orderld}{KuCoin Get Stop Order By OrderId}

Verified: 2026-02-01
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Order Verification}: Confirm a stop order was placed with the correct parameters after submission.
\item \strong{Status Monitoring}: Poll order status to detect when a stop order has been triggered.
\item \strong{Audit Trail}: Retrieve full order details for logging and post-trade analysis.
}
}

